title: Brand New Apartment In Garland/Richardson Area!
posting_body: ['Luxury community is located within minutes of The Firewheel Town Center, which includes numerous shops and restaurants.', 'Featuring an astounding selection of sixteen unique floor plans.', 'Brand new community offers comfort, convenience, and an overall luxurious experience that will encourage you to call us home for years to come.', 'Residents enjoy our resort-style swimming pool, elegant clubhouse, and “grab-n-go” breakfast and coffee bar', 'Community Features....', '• Spacious Gourmet Kitchens with Granite and Quartz Countertops', '• Stainless Steel Whirlpool Appliance Package', '• Two Designed Color Cabinet Packages', '• Side-By-Side, Frost-Free Refrigerator*', '• Flat Top, Electric Range/Oven Combination', '• Kitchen Islands*', '• Professionally Designed Color Schemes', '• Ten Foot and Tray Ceilings', '• Elegant Double Crown Molding', '• Vinyl Plank Flooring*', '• Upgraded Cut Pile Carpets', '• Built-In Bookcases/Desks/ Entertainment Centers*', '• Designer Ceramic Tile Floors in Kitchen and Bath', '• French Door Refrigerator with Bottom Freezer*', '• 36” Vanity Height Cabinets with Double Sinks*', '• Garden Tubs and Standup Shower*', '• Vintage Calacatta Tile Backsplash', '• In-Wall, High Speed Internet/Media Cabling', '• USB Ports', '• Digital Intrusion Alarm System Offer 2G', '*Available in select units', 'Please Call Desiree with DASH Apartment Locators', 'show contact info', 'Mention Ad M112']
